Theodore von Eltz https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theodore_von_Eltz 0 Theodore von Eltz (November 5, 1893 – October 6, 1964) was an American film actor. He appeared in more than 200 films between 1915 and 1957. He was the father of actress Lori March. Theodore_von_Eltz ( November_5_,_1893 – October_6_,_1964 ) was an_American_film_actor .
